title: Cascading parameter values not displayed properly in HTML viewer
description: Cascading parameter values are not being displayed properly in the HTML viewer. When the first parameter value is selected, the second parameter value in the same cascading parameter group should be displayed, but it is not.
OB: When selecting the first parameter value in the cascading parameter group, the second parameter value should be displayed in the HTML viewer.
EB: The second parameter value in the cascading parameter group is not being displayed in the HTML viewer when the first parameter value is selected.
SR: Ensure that the HTML viewer properly displays the second parameter value in the cascading parameter group when the first parameter value is selected.
